<Project>
  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFrameworks>net8.0;net10.0</TargetFrameworks>
    <LangVersion>preview</LangVersion>
    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>
    <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>
    <InvariantGlobalization>false</InvariantGlobalization>
    <TreatWarningsAsErrors>true</TreatWarningsAsErrors>
    <Version>1.4.20</Version>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>
      Conformance: non-streaming type/serialization correctness and more streaming breadth. fn:available-system-properties now returns a sequence of xs:QName (was a single non-QName item, failing binding to xs:QName*). A variable/parameter/function with as="ATOMIC-TYPE" and a temporary-tree or node-valued body now atomizes and casts to the declared atomic type (date/time/duration/anyURI/untypedAtomic/etc.) instead of leaving a raw result-tree-fragment — node-typed as= keeps its nodes. Invalid xsl:output / xsl:result-document / disable-output-escaping values now raise XTSE0020 instead of being silently ignored. Streaming: a streamed xsl:copy / copy-of preserves in-scope namespace declarations and prefixes; xsl:for-each whose select is a conditional (if(…) then … else …) streams the selected branch; a wildcard-attribute existence climb (ancestor::*/@*) streams; and a consuming attribute sequence (data(@x)) atomizes correctly in a streamed copy. Requires PhoenixmlDb.Core 1.2.2 and PhoenixmlDb.XQuery 1.5.4. No API changes. See RELEASES.md for full notes.
    </PackageReleaseNotes>
    <NoWarn>$(NoWarn);CS1591</NoWarn>
    <EnforceCodeStyleInBuild>true</EnforceCodeStyleInBuild>
    <AnalysisLevel>latest-all</AnalysisLevel>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <PropertyGroup>
    <Authors>Endpoint Systems</Authors>
    <Company>Endpoint Systems</Company>
    <Product>PhoenixmlDb</Product>
    <Copyright>Copyright © Endpoint Systems 2026. All rights reserved.</Copyright>
    <RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
    <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/phoenixmldb/phoenixmldb-xslt</RepositoryUrl>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://phoenixml.dev</PackageProjectUrl>
    <PackageLicenseExpression>Apache-2.0</PackageLicenseExpression>
    <PackageIcon>icon.png</PackageIcon>
    <PackageReadmeFile>PACKAGE.md</PackageReadmeFile>
    <GenerateDocumentationFile>true</GenerateDocumentationFile>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <None Include="$(MSBuildThisFileDirectory)icon.png" Pack="true" PackagePath="" />
    <None Include="$(MSBuildThisFileDirectory)PACKAGE.md" Pack="true" PackagePath="" />
  </ItemGroup>

  <PropertyGroup Condition="'$(Configuration)' == 'Release'">
    <DebugType>embedded</DebugType>
    <DebugSymbols>true</DebugSymbols>
    <Deterministic>true</Deterministic>
  </PropertyGroup>
</Project>
